                <hr>
                <h3 id="mageia.org">Mageia.Org</h3>
                <p>is the French, Paris-based legal structure supporting the Mageia project. </p>                <ul><li><a href="./constitution/">Mageia.Org's legal constitution</a> and <a href="https://wiki.mageia.org/en/Org">governance</a> rules; </li><li><a href="../about/reports/">financial reports</a>, <a href="../thank-you/">donators</a>. </li></ul>

